<p>
<note n="0104007" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0104007">體＝顯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【石】</note>
<note n="0105002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0105002">因＝同【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0105005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0105005">謂＝誰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0105010" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0105010">位＝住【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0106002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0106002">彼＝破【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，<!--CBETA todo type: i-->破我品 Ātmavāda-pratiṣedha.</note>
<note n="0106003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0106003">雨＝兩【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0107002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0107002">於＝謂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【石】</note>
<note n="0107005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0107005">恃＝情【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
