<note n="0107008" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0107008">或＝惑【流布本】</note>
<note n="0107009" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0107009">瀑＝暴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0107012" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0107012">說＝欲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0107017" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0107017">獨＝猛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0107018" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0107018">纏＝種【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【石】</note>
